readable.content: A man talks to a woman wearing a backpack . A woman with a bag talks to a man on a bicycle near a street . Man riding a bicycle as woman walks beside him on a street . The woman carrying a backpack is facing the camera , while the man is turned away . The woman in the white shirt and black backpack is walking with the man in the blue shirt .
